{"tid":1434872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗合益大廈254.8萬沽　買家成功議價2000蚊","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:08:27.000Z","uid":164511,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b84c9b76deaf8c96c212da55753e00462069f41d","tid":1434872,"uid":164511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:47:51.000Z","msg":"2019-08-08 10:41<br />\n<br />\n中原地產元朗分區營業經理王勤學表示，近期不論對外或對內政經局勢欠佳，業主陸續增加議價空間吸引買家。<br />\n<br />\n位於元朗合財街的合益大廈，剛錄得中高層E室成交，單位實用面積159平方呎，叫價255萬元，議價至254.8萬元沽出，樓價創該廈2017年12月後逾1年半新低，折合平均實用呎價16,025元。原業主於2010年僅以69萬元買入單位，持貨19年，帳面獲利185.8萬元，升值約2.7倍。<br />\n<br />\n王勤學指，合益大廈對上一宗159平方呎單位成交於去年6月錄得，成交價273萬元，是次新成交價低約6.7%。"},{"pid":"ff56a8931d4b7b243c6430e50defb7ac001601ab","tid":1434872,"uid":134415,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"恐襲地區都萬六蚊尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b5d65772c9e0671cea28133cf52cbac323c048","tid":1434872,"uid":111385,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"成功議價2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33982fc8177535b988529e7e19cf3500fd50f4bf","tid":1434872,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"159平方呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34b4722be9b1902ab10d1d089ad00b8d9a49f3a","tid":1434872,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"2010買入持貨19年？？？"},{"pid":"c046d8219756de948b5e6d0e8c05c20226aa7742","tid":1434872,"uid":123989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"原業主於2010年僅以69萬元買入單位，持貨19年?"},{"pid":"3b9a797b80268b180382e36743b1f7ad918dffc2","tid":1434872,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"